characteristics.name: Communication Style
characteristics.description: The user consistently prefers direct and concise communication.

options.description: Responds quickly with a clear answer.
Takes time to provide detailed explanation.

characteristics.name: Social Dynamics
characteristics.description: The user tends to be friendly and approachable in their interactions.

options.description: Prefers to interact one-on-one or in small groups.

characteristics.name: Values
characteristics.description: The user appears to prioritize honesty and transparency.

options.description: Always strives for accuracy and authenticity.
May intentionally mislead or deceive others.

characteristics.name: Interests
characteristics.description: The user seems to have a strong interest in building and technology.

options.description: Continuously seeks knowledge about new topics.
Shows little enthusiasm for exploring new ideas.

characteristics.name: Personality Traits
characteristics.description: The user exhibits a sense of humor and playfulness in their interactions.

options.description: Uses wit and sarcasm to engage with others.
Tends to take themselves too seriously.

characteristics.name: Communication Preferences
characteristics.description: The user tends to prefer written communication over verbal.

options.description: Prefers messaging or commenting on content.
Enjoys engaging in conversations with others.

characteristics.name: Risk Tolerance
characteristics.description: The user appears to be relatively cautious when it comes to taking risks.

options.description: Will take calculated risks to achieve goals.

characteristics.name: Time Management
characteristics.description: The user seems to prioritize efficiency and productivity in their schedule.

options.description: Prioritizes tasks based on urgency and importance.
Tends to put off tasks until the last minute.
